profile:
Green Side Up Environmental Services (GSU) is a landscape contracting company specializing in conventional landscaping construction (residential and commercial) and ecological restoration landscape construction such as retaining walls, patios, stairs, walkways, gardens, fences, decks and design.  We provide services for all levels of government, the private sector, and non-government organizations (NGO's). Other ecological services we provide include Managed Forest Tax Incentive Plans (MFTIPS), landscape construction and design, ecological resTortoration, Native plant nursery, and forestry.
